# Skill manifest

This repository enumerates agent `SKILL.md` files under the default discovery roots (`infrastructure/` and, when that tree exists, `projects/cognitive_case_diagrams/src/`) into `.cursor/skill_manifest.json` (sibling of this `rules/` folder): each entry has `name`, `description`, `path`, and `cursor_at` (use as `@path` in Cursor). See `infrastructure/skills/discovery.py` (`DEFAULT_SKILL_SEARCH_ROOTS`).

After adding, renaming, or editing skill frontmatter, regenerate:

```bash
uv run python -m infrastructure.skills write
```

Validate the file matches the tree:

```bash
uv run python -m infrastructure.skills check
```

Programmatic access: `from infrastructure.skills import discover_skills` with the repository root `Path`.
